### Test 1: Call API without token (should get 401 Unauthorized)
POST http://localhost:5159/api/CardPayment/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "4532015112830366"
}

### Test 2: Call API with invalid token (should get 403 Forbidden)
POST http://localhost:5159/api/CardPayment/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-xyz

{
  "cardNumber": "4532015112830366"
}

### Test 3: Call API with valid token (should get 200 OK)
POST http://localhost:5159/api/CardPayment/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer dev-token-123456

{
  "cardNumber": "4532015112830366"
}

### Test 4: Call API with valid token without Bearer prefix (should get 200 OK)
POST http://localhost:5159/api/CardPayment/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: test-token-abcdef

{
  "cardNumber": "5425233430109903"
}

### Test 5: Health check without token (should get 200 OK - no auth required)
GET http://localhost:5159/api/CardPayment/health

